# 一些脚本



P已知高位攻击

```
n 
pbar 
kbits =384
PR.<x> = PolynomialRing(Zmod(n))
f = x + pbar
x0 = f.small_roots(X=2^kbits, beta=0.4)[0]
p = x0 + pbar
print(p)
q = n // int(p)
print(q)
```



# 草稿区


$$
n = p*q  \\
\phi = (p-1)*(q-1) \\
(1314*p-520*q)^{phi+1} \equiv 1314*p-520*q
$$
